{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                                              // hydrogen // schema // media"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Media pillar — Video, Audio, Image, Upload, and Gallery state management."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Design Philosophy"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Media playback and manipulation are modeled as pure state + commands."},{"LineComment":" | No JavaScript APIs (HTMLMediaElement, Canvas, File API) leak into"},{"LineComment":" | these modules. The runtime interprets commands against actual browser"},{"LineComment":" | APIs, enabling:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - Deterministic testing of media UIs"},{"LineComment":" | - Server-side rendering of media player state"},{"LineComment":" | - Agent composition of media interfaces"},{"LineComment":" | - Reproducible behavior across platforms"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Submodules"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### Video Playback"},{"LineComment":" | - `Hydrogen.Schema.Media.Video` — Video playback state and commands"},{"LineComment":" |   - Volume (0.0-1.0), PlaybackRate (0.25-4.0), Seconds"},{"LineComment":" |   - VideoState, VideoCommand, BufferedRange"},{"LineComment":" |   - Fullscreen, mute, seek, play/pause"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### Audio Playback"},{"LineComment":" | - `Hydrogen.Schema.Media.Audio` — Audio playback state and commands"},{"LineComment":" |   - Re-exports shared types from Video"},{"LineComment":" |   - AudioState, AudioCommand, AudioTrack"},{"LineComment":" |   - Playlist management, playback modes"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### Image Manipulation"},{"LineComment":" | - `Hydrogen.Schema.Media.Image` — Image editing state"},{"LineComment":" |   - CropArea, CropState, FlipState"},{"LineComment":" |   - Rotation (0-360 degrees), ScaleFactor (0.1-10.0)"},{"LineComment":" |   - Zoom, rotate, flip, crop operations"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### File Upload"},{"LineComment":" | - `Hydrogen.Schema.Media.Upload` — File upload state"},{"LineComment":" |   - FileEntry, UploadState, UploadProgress"},{"LineComment":" |   - Validation, configuration, error handling"},{"LineComment":" |   - Multi-file upload with progress tracking"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ### Gallery/Lightbox"},{"LineComment":" | - `Hydrogen.Schema.Media.Gallery` — Gallery state"},{"LineComment":" |   - MediaItem (images, videos), GalleryState"},{"LineComment":" |   - Navigation, slideshow, thumbnails"},{"LineComment":" |   - Fullscreen lightbox mode"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Bounded Types"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | All media types use bounded primitives:"},{"LineComment":" | - Volume: clamped [0.0, 1.0]"},{"LineComment":" | - PlaybackRate: clamped [0.25, 4.0]"},{"LineComment":" | - Rotation: wrapping [0, 360)"},{"LineComment":" | - ScaleFactor: clamped [0.1, 10.0]"},{"LineComment":" | - Progress: clamped [0.0, 1.0]"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Usage"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ```purescript"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Media.Video as Video"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Media.Audio as Audio"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Media.Image as Image"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Media.Upload as Upload"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Media.Gallery as Gallery"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Video player state"},{"LineComment":" | videoState = Video.initialVideoState (Video.seconds 120.0)"},{"LineComment":" | videoState' = Video.applyCommand Video.Play videoState"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Audio player with playlist"},{"LineComment":" | playlist = Audio.addTrack track1 (Audio.emptyPlaylist \"My Playlist\")"},{"LineComment":" | playlistState = Audio.initialPlaylistState playlist"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Image crop state"},{"LineComment":" | cropState = Image.initialCropState 1920.0 1080.0"},{"LineComment":" | cropState' = Image.applyImageCommand Image.RotateCW cropState"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- File upload"},{"LineComment":" | uploadState = Upload.addFile fileEntry Upload.initialUploadState"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Gallery"},{"LineComment":" | gallery = Gallery.galleryFromItems [item1, item2, item3]"},{"LineComment":" | gallery' = Gallery.applyGalleryCommand Gallery.Next gallery"},{"LineComment":" | ```"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## At Billion-Agent Scale"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | These primitives enable deterministic media interfaces:"},{"LineComment":" | - Same VideoState = same player UI across all agents"},{"LineComment":" | - Same CropState = same image transform, always"},{"LineComment":" | - Same GalleryState = same gallery display"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | No JavaScript API variability. No browser differences."},{"LineComment":" | Pure data describing media state."}],"decls":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[104,23],"start":[104,1]}},"bindType":"NonRec","expression":{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[105,23],"start":[105,16]}},"type":"Literal","value":{"literalType":"StringLiteral","value":"0.1.0"}},"identifier":"mediaVersion"}],"exports":["mediaVersion"],"foreign":[],"imports":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[105,23],"start":[99,1]}},"moduleName":["Prim"]}],"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Media"],"modulePath":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Media.purs","reExports":{},"sourceSpan":{"end":[105,23],"start":[99,1]}}